### Exemplos de chamadas à API de Autenticação
### Base URL: http://localhost:5026 ou https://localhost:7115

### 1. LOGIN - Autenticar usuário (João Silva)
POST http://localhost:5026/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao.silva@example.com",
  "password": "Senha123!"
}

###

### 2. LOGIN - Autenticar usuário (Maria Santos)
POST http://localhost:5026/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria.santos@example.com",
  "password": "Senha456!"
}

###

### 3. REFRESH TOKEN - Renovar token de acesso
### Substitua {refreshToken} pelo token retornado no login
POST http://localhost:5026/api/Auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{refreshToken}"
}

###

### 4. RESET PASSWORD - Redefinir senha
POST http://localhost:5026/api/Auth/resetpassword
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao.silva@example.com",
  "newPassword": "NovaSenha123!",
  "resetToken": null
}

###

### 5. LOGIN - Teste com credenciais inválidas (deve retornar 401)
POST http://localhost:5026/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario.inexistente@example.com",
  "password": "SenhaErrada123!"
}

###

